'''夜鸚鵡'''（[[学名|学名]]：''{{lang|la|Pezoporus occidentalis}}''），又名'''夜行鸚鵡'''，是[[澳洲|澳洲]]特有的一種細小[[鸚鵡|鸚鵡]]。牠們原先是分類在獨自的[[屬|屬]]中（''Geopsittacus''）<ref>{{Cite book en|author=Forshaw, Joseph M. & Cooper, William T.|year=1981|title=Parrots of the World|edition=3rd ed|publisher=Press, Willoughby|location=Australia}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book en|author=Gould J.|title=Handbook to the Birds of Australia|location=London|year=1865|publisher=Lansdowne Press}}</ref>，但很多學者都將牠們連同[[地棲鸚鵡|地棲鸚鵡]]分類在''Pezoporus''之中。<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Leeton, Peter R. J., Christidis, Leslie, Westerman, Michael & Boles, Walter E.|year=1994|title=Molecular phylogenetic relationships of the Night Parrot (''Geopsittacus occidentalis'') and the Ground Parrot (''Pezoporus wallicus'')|journal=Auk|volume=111|issue=4|pages=833-843|url=http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Auk/v111n04/p0833-p0843.pdf|access-date=2009-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110613174526/http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Auk/v111n04/p0833-p0843.pdf|archive-date=2011-06-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[虎皮鸚鵡|虎皮鸚鵡]]亦是牠們的遠親。

於1912年至1979年沒有見到夜鸚鵡，引起認為牠們已經[[滅絕|滅絕]]的推測。自1979年就已經極少見到牠們，而牠們的數量不明。最近一次的活體觀察記錄是在2017年，於[[西澳大利亞|西澳大利亞]]的[[布魯姆_(西澳大利亞)|布魯姆]]被拍攝到。

== 特徵 ==
夜鸚鵡較為細小，主要呈黃綠色，有深褐色、黑色及黃色的斑點。牠們的尾巴較[[地棲鸚鵡|地棲鸚鵡]]的短，而棲息地及分佈亦有所不同。牠們主要是領域性的，只會在受驚或尋找水源時才會飛到空中。牠們主要在夜間活動，且鬼鬼祟祟。牠們喜歡生活在[[澳洲|澳洲]]內陸的乾旱地方。

== 保育狀況 ==
[[File:Night-Parrot-dist.svg|缩略图]]
夜鸚鵡的數量不明，估計狀況介乎[[滅絕|滅絕]]至無危。[[世界自然保護聯盟|世界自然保護聯盟]]將牠們列為瀕危。

自1880年代起，就只有少量可靠的觀察報告，最近的是於2006年在[[昆士蘭|昆士蘭]]西南部發現夜鸚鵡的屍體標本。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/news/national/twitchers-cry-foul-in-case-of-the-deceased-parrot/2007/06/22/1182019367467.html.com?page=fullpage#contentSwap1 |title = Twitchers cry foul in case of the deceased parrot |work = Brisbane Times |accessdate = 2008-04-09 |date = 2007-06-23 |archive-date = 2016-03-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304234438/http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/news/national/twitchers-cry-foul-in-case-of-the-deceased-parrot/2007/06/22/1182019367467.html.com?page=fullpage#contentSwap1 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200702/s1850780.htm|title=Ex-parrot sighting in Qld sparks interest|author=Australian Broadcasting Corporation|date=2007-02-19|accessdate=2007-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070220092024/http://www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200702/s1850780.htm|archive-date=2007-02-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=roberts>{{Cite web|author=Roberts, Greg|url=http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,20867,21234252-30417,00.html|title=Bad news for one night parrot, good for species|work=The Australian|date=2007-02-16|accessdate=2007-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070217112826/http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,20867,21234252-30417,00.html|archive-date=2007-02-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>之前於2005年，在[[西澳州|西澳州]]的[[皮爾巴拉|皮爾巴拉]]觀察到三隻夜鸚鵡。<ref name=roberts/><ref>{{cite journal en |last=Davis |first=Robert A. |coauthors=Brenden M. Metcalf |year=2008 |title=The Night Parrot (''Pezoporus occidentalis'') in northern Western Australia: a recent sighting from the Pilbara region |journal=Emu |volume=108 |issue=3 |pages=233-236 |doi=10.1071/MU07058 |accessdate=2008-11-08 }}</ref>於1990年在[[昆士蘭|昆士蘭]]的偏遠地區亦發現了一隻屍體<ref name=roberts/><ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Boles, Walter E.; Longmore, N. W. & Thompson, M. C.|year=1994|title=A Recent Specimen of the Night Parrot ''Geopsittacus occidentalis''|journal=Emu|volume=94|issue=1|pages=37-40|doi=10.1071/MU9940037|url=http://www.publish.csiro.au/nid/96/paper/MU9940037.htm|access-date=2009-01-15|archive-date=2012-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016113954/http://www.publish.csiro.au/nid/96/paper/MU9940037.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，及於1979年一隊[[南澳博物館|南澳博物館]]的[[科學家|科學家]]在[[南澳州|南澳州]]北部見到一群類似的夜鸚鵡。[[鳥類學家|鳥類學家]]一直在尋找活生生的夜鸚鵡，甚至在[[斑胸草雀|斑胸草雀]]的巢中去尋找夜鸚鵡的[[羽毛|羽毛]]。

